author: jonesde
msg: Some improvements for password encryption based on ml discussions: now supports reading weird old password hex conversion, plus a more standard/correct hex conversion using Apache Commons Codex Hex class, plus an attempt to encode using a hash type in a prefix in the database; will always save the encoded password using the default type specified in the config file and will put a hash type prefix on it for portability
